GSD.product_version: versions from v4.11 to before v6.0.3
GSD.description:
crypto: cavium - prevent integer overflow loading firmware

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.3 by commit e29fd7a6852376d2cfb95ad5d6d3eeff93f815e9, it was introduced in version v4.11 by commit 9e2c7d99941d000a36f68a3594cec27a1bbea274. For more details please see the references link.
